  },
  {
   "type": "raw",
   "tag": "div",
   "attrs": {
    "class": "prof"
   },
   "html": "\n衆議院議員、大政翼賛会常任総務、東京朝日新聞記者"
  },
  {
   "type": "raw",
   "tag": "table",
   "attrs": {
    "class": "off"
   },
   "html": "<tbody><tr><td class=\"lt\"><a href.html\"=\"\">　</a></td><td class=\"lt\"><a href.html\"=\"\">　</a></td><td class=\"lt\"><a href.html\"=\"\">　</a></td><td class=\"lt\"><a href.html\"=\"\">　</a></td></tr></tbody>"
  },
  {
   "type": "raw",
   "tag": "div",
   "attrs": {
    "class": "off"
   },
   "html": "<span class=\"m_r\">エピソード 1</span>調査中。"
  },
  {
   "type": "raw",
   "tag": "div",
   "attrs": {
    "class": "hidden"
   },
   "html": "<a name=\"s1\"></a>\n<a href=\"#s1\">＝</a><a href=\"#h\">△</a><a href=\"#h\">◎</a><a href=\"#s2\">▽</a><a href=\"#s1\">＝</a>"
  },
  {
   "type": "timeline",
   "rows": [
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　福岡県出身。早稲田大学卒業後、東京朝日新聞記者を経て、衆議院議員。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　<a href=\"../p/ituyosi.html\">犬養毅</a>を尊敬し革新倶楽部に入党、のち憲政会、民政党。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　<a href=\"../1931/waka2_1.html\">若槻内閣②</a>が<a href=\"../1931/waka2_9.html\">閣内不統一で総辞職</a>すると、<a href=\"../p/akenzo.html\">安達謙蔵</a>らと国民同盟を結成。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　国家社会主義に傾き、東方会を結成。解党後、大政翼賛会常任総務、のち辞任。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　戦時刑事特別法改正を契機に<a href=\"../1941/tojo_1.html\">東條内閣</a>と対立。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　<a href=\"../1943/01nakan.html\">朝日新聞に寄稿した「戦時宰相論」</a>は<a href=\"../p/thideki.html\">東條</a>を激怒させる。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　<a href=\"../1943/10nakan.html\">倒閣容疑で逮捕</a>され、釈放直後に自刃。"
      }
     ]
    }
   ]
  },
